<doc>
  <member name="D3D12_CLEAR_FLAGS">
    <summary>
      <para>Specifies what to clear from the depth stencil view.</para>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>This enum is used by <see cref="ID3D12GraphicsCommandList.ClearDepthStencilView" />.
The flags can be combined to clear all.</para>
    </remarks>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d12/direct3d-12-enumerations">Core Enumerations</seealso>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_CLEAR_FLAGS.D3D12_CLEAR_FLAG_DEPTH">
    <summary>
      <para>Indicates the depth buffer should be cleared.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_CLEAR_FLAGS.D3D12_CLEAR_FLAG_STENCIL">
    <summary>
      <para>Indicates the stencil buffer should be cleared.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
</doc>